>code</span><span>&gt;&lt;/</span><span>pre</span><span>&gt;</span></div><div>            <span>&lt;/</span><span>div</span><span>&gt;</span></div><br><div>            <span>&lt;!-- ট্যাগ সেকশন --&gt;</span></div><div>            <span>&lt;</span><span>div</span> <span>class</span><span>=</span><span>\"pt-8 border-t border-gray-200 flex flex-wrap gap-2\"</span><span>&gt;</span></div><div>                <span>&lt;</span><span>span</span> <span>class</span><span>=</span><span>\"bg-gray-200 text-gray-700 px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm hover:bg-blue-100 hover:text-blue-700 cursor-pointer transition\"</span><span>&gt;</span>#ব্লগিং<span>&lt;/</span><span>span</span><span>&gt;</span></div><div>                <span>&lt;</span><span>span</span> <span>class</span><span>=</span><span>\"bg-gray-200 text-gray-700 px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm hover:bg-blue-100 hover:text-blue-700 cursor-pointer transition\"</span><span>&gt;</span>#টিপস<span>&lt;/</span><span>span</span><span>&gt;</span></div><div>                <span>&lt;</span><span>span</span> <span>class</span><span>=</span><span>\"bg-gray-200 text-gray-700 px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm hover:bg-blue-100 hover:text-blue-700 cursor-pointer transition\"</span><span>&gt;</span>#ক্যারিয়ার<span>&lt;/</span><span>span</span><span>&gt;</span></div><div>            <span>&lt;/</span><span>div</span><span>&gt;</span></div><br><div>            <span>&lt;!-- কমেন্ট সেকশন টেস্ট --&gt;</span></div><div>            <span>&lt;</span><span>section</span> <span>class</span><span>=</span><span>\"bg-white p-6 rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-gray-100 mt-10\"</span><span>&gt;</span></div><div>                <span>&lt;</span><span>h4</span> <span>class</span><span>=</span><span>\"text-xl font-bold mb-6\"</span><span>&gt;</span>আপনার মন্তব্য জানান<span>&lt;/</span><span>h4</span><span>&gt;</span></div><div>                <span>&lt;</span><span>textarea</span> <span>class</span><span>=</span><span>\"w-full p-4 border border-gray-200 rounded-lg focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-500 outline-none mb-4\"</span> <span>rows</span><span>=</span><span>\"4\"</span> <span>placeholder</span><span>=</span><span>\"এখানে লিখুন...\"</span><span>&gt;&lt;/</span><span>textarea</span><span>&gt;</span></div><div>                <span>&lt;</span><span>button</span> <span>class</span><span>=</span><span>\"bg-blue-600 text-white px-6 py-2 rounded-lg font-semibold hover:bg-blue-700 transition\"</span><span>&gt;</span>মন্তব্য সাবমিট করুন<span>&lt;/</span><span>button</span><span>&gt;</span></div><div>            <span>&lt;/</span><span>section</span><span>&gt;</span></div><div>        <span>&lt;/</span><span>article</span><span>&gt;</span></div><br><div>        <span>&lt;!-- সাইডবার এলাকা --&gt;</span></div><div>        <span>&lt;</span><span>aside</span> <span>class</span><span>=</span><span>\"space-y-10\"</span><span>&gt;</span></div><div>            <span>&lt;!-- লেখক পরিচিতি --&gt;</span></div><div>            <span>&lt;</span><span>div</span> <span>class</span><span>=</span><span>\"bg-white p-6 rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-gray-100\"</span><span>&gt;</span></div><div>                <span>&lt;</span><span>h4</span> <span>class</span><span>=</span><span>\"text-lg font-bold mb-4 border-b pb-2\"</span><span>&gt;</span>লেখকের পরিচিতি<span>&lt;/</span><span>h4</span><span>&gt;</span></div><div>                <span>&lt;</span><span>div</span> <span>class</span><span>=</span><span>\"flex items-center space-x-4\"</span><span>&gt;</span></div><div>                    <span>&lt;</span><span>div</span> <span>class</span><span>=</span><span>\"w-16 h-16 bg-blue-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-blue-600 font-bold text-xl\"</span><span>&gt;</span>ইউ<span>&lt;/</span><span>div</span><span>&gt;</span></div><div>                    <span>&lt;</span><span>div</span><span>&gt;</span></div><div>                        <span>&lt;</span><span>p</span> <span>class</span><span>=</span><span>\"font-bold\"</span><span>